            <span class="story-tag">Why it stands out</span>
            <h3>Positioned for both lifestyle appeal and investment confidence.</h3>
            <p>
              The inventory is suited to buyers looking for a future-ready apartment with strong road visibility, established neighborhood infrastructure, and a gated community environment.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-8">
          <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <article class="story-card">
                <div class="icon-wrap"><i class="fa-solid fa-road"></i></div>
                <h3>Prime NH-152 frontage</h3>
                <p>Located directly on the Ambala-Chandigarh Expressway for easier daily movement and strong future visibility.</p>
              </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <article class="story-card">
                <div class="icon-wrap"><i class="fa-solid fa-city"></i></div>
                <h3>Contemporary construction approach</h3>
                <p>Mivan construction technology supports a cleaner execution standard and a more premium structural identity.</p>
              </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <article class="story-card">
                <div class="icon-wrap"><i class="fa-solid fa-school"></i></div>
                <h3>Everyday convenience nearby</h3>
                <p>Set beside major educational and healthcare institutions, with an established township opposite the site.</p>
              </article>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <article class="story-card">
                <div class="icon-wrap"><i class="fa-solid fa-wallet"></i></div>
                <h3>Bank loan support available</h3>
                <p>Structured for buyers who want smoother financing, attractive payment planning, and guided booking assistance.</p>
              </article>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-shell section-dark">
